Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:09.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}Sva sama, zalutala sam na svom putovanju.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:17.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Samo srce mi se kretalo, dok sam u mestu stajala.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:25.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ali sada, ponovo, mogu pešačiti daleko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:34.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Da, otkako sam na ovom putu tebe upoznala.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:42.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepoznata pesma koju putnici pevaju,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:52.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,ima nostalgičan prizvuk kada god sam sa tobom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:01:01.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako svet koji sam videla u snovima postoji negde,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:09.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,potražimo ga, poneseni vetrovima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:13.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ledena zora,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:18.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasušeno podne,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:22.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ili noć puna strepnje,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:28.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Pogledajmo šta dolazi na kraju.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:05.00,K6Reklama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ovo izdanje nije namenjeno prodaji ili iznajmljivanju!\NOVO JE BESPLATAN FANSUB!\Nhttp://www.anime-overdose.com
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:09.00,K6Reklama,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Obrada i prevod: Knez Miloš
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:43.25,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Od davnina u ovom selu,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:50.03,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kada vetar zanjiše žito, govorilo se da vuk trči kraj njega.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:54.34,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kada bi vetar oborio stabljike žita, to je bio vuk koji ih je gazio,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:57.48,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}a za siromašne žetve su krivili vukov nezasit apetit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:03.65,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U početku nije bilo ničega. Postojala je samo toplina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:08.24,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Onda je sačinjeno obećanje.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:28.67,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Susreti i rastanci su se ponavljali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:34.48,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ljudi su vremenom stekli sposobnost da obezbede blagostanje samo svojom veštinom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:40.41,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možda više nemaju potrebu da održe obećanje.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:45.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vuk i najbolja odeća
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:51.13,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dojadili su više seoski putevi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:52.63,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.26,Dialogue,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Putujući trgovac?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:03.51,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na pola dana puta ka istoku se nalazi jedno malo selo u planinama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:05.62,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tamo sam trgovao solju.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.24,Dialogue,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Znači ovo je sve so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:07.73,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nije.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:11.37,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo su krzna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.74,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, to je samo svežanj žita.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.74,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je sorta koja je otporna i na toplo i na hladno vreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:21.37,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta se dešava?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.89,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Atmosfera ovde je napetija nego obično.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:28.37,Dialogue,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da će se u selu na zapadu održati paganska svečanost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:29.60,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pagani?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:35.05,Dialogue,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Drznici koji ne veruju u našeg svemogućeg Boga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:39.87,Dialogue,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mislim da bi Papa trebao da primeni više sile, kao što je činio u prošlosti,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.74,Dialogue,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ali čini se da ne može da ih drži pod kontrolom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.98,Dialogue,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sigurno ga varaju svojim obmanama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:46.50,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pagani, kaže?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.47,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stanovnici Pasroea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:54.60,Dialogue,Farmer A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, gospodine Lorens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.67,Dialogue,Farmer B,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stvarno sam bio iznenađen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:59.65,Dialogue,Farmer B,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ko bi pomislio da će ovaj novi metod doneti ovakvu obilnu žetvu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.24,Dialogue,Farmer C,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sve je to zahvaljujući Grofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:04.17,Dialogue,Farmer D,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne možeš se osloniti na vuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:07.28,Dialogue,Farmer C,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, pazi šta govoriš. On bi trebao biti božanstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.96,Dialogue,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zdravo, gospodine Lorens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.33,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dobar dan. Davno se nismo videli.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:15.59,Dialogue,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Došao si u pravo vreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:18.09,Dialogue,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sutra počinje festival žetve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:22.06,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sutra? Meni izgleda kao da je već počeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:25.26,Dialogue,Villager B,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Istina je, ovde smo malo požurili sa slavljem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:25.97,Dialogue,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta kažeš na koju turu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:29.94,Dialogue,Villager C,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, hej. Gospodin Lorens nije takav kao što smo mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.15,Dialogue,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A, pa izvinjavam se onda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:36.52,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nego, znate li gde je Kloe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.48,Dialogue,Villager D,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kloe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.95,Dialogue,Villager D,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A tako. Znači o tome se radi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:42.12,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ona je samo moj šegrt u ovom poslu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:45.55,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mislio sam da popijemo koje piće za stara vremena.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.86,Dialogue,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemaš sreće.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:51.74,Dialogue,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tamo su imali najmanje prinosa ove godine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:54.25,Dialogue,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}pa će možda ona biti Horo ovog festivala.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:00.79,Dialogue,Villager E,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pogledajte tamo! Vuk leži prikriven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:04.61,Dialogue,Villager F,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ko će da uhvati vuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.67,Dialogue,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eto ga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:07.73,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kloe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.15,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lorens!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:12.89,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Došao si!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:15.11,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako ne budeš pazila Horo će da ti pobegne!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.66,Dialogue,Villager G,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo je zadnji svežanj.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:21.08,Dialogue,Villager H,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne krije li neko pohlepan žito?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:23.39,Dialogue,Villager I,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pazi se! Horo će pobeći!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.76,Dialogue,Villager G,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ko je uhvatio vuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.88,Dialogue,Villager G,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kloe, Kloe, Kloe je!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:54.03,Dialogue,Villager G,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vuk Horo se pojavio! Uhvatite je! Uhvatite je!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.19,Dialogue,Villager G,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pobeći će tamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.46,Dialogue,Villager J,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gospodine Lorens, uhvatite je!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.14,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pošto se nismo odavno videli, očekujem da ti častiš večeras.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:16.12,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta to treba da znači?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.62,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bićeš zaglavljena tu nedelju dana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:31.14,Dialogue,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zahvaljujući tebi smo našli mnogo novih mogućnosti za trgovinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:36.18,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da Kloe obavlja dobar posao kao seoski pregovarač.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:39.41,Dialogue,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aha, stvarno obavlja dobar posao.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:41.72,Dialogue,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo selo se sprema za nagle promene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.91,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, srebrnjaci iz Torrenija.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.86,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nisu tako česti u ovoj oblasti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:52.06,Dialogue,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oprostili smo se od prljavih i zarđalih srebrnjaka iz Lutea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.62,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da se spremate približiti velikim gradovima kao što je Patsio u bližoj budućnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.88,Dialogue,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Imamo mi još posla do tada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:03.91,Dialogue,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U svakom slučaju, sve dugujemo novom vlastelinu, Grofu Erendot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:07.17,Dialogue,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Više nema potrebe da se molimo vuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:11.85,Dialogue,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moć čoveka je nadvladala suše i oluje.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:17.07,Dialogue,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Voleo bih da napunimo kovčege Lumione zlatnicima umesto Torreny srebrnjacima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:20.67,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Molim da poslujete sa mnom i kada dođete dotle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.92,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Autsajder bi samo smetao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:45.00,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Osim toga, još je rano da razmišljaju o Lumione zlatnicima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:51.26,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, mogao bih odspavati.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:20.97,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemoguće...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:25.74,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Hej ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.73,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}P-Probudi se!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:39.01,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta radiš u mojim kolima?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.44,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rekao sam ti da se probudiš!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.19,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-Tvoje uši...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.43,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:48.31,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mesec je krasan, nije li?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:52.00,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej ti, da nemaš možda nekog pića pri sebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.12,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}N-Nemam ništa takvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:57.80,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A i pre svega...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:01.46,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tako znači? Onda nešto za jelo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.85,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah. Kakva šteta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:12.94,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.78,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jesi li posednuta đavolom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.27,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kakav si nezahvalnik,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.03,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}da uperiš svoj mač u mene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.85,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Š-Šta si rekla?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.58,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, tako je. Ti nisi iz ovog sela.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.84,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izvini, zaboravila sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:38.09,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moje ime je Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:41.06,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Davno nisam preuzela ovo obličje,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.85,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ali izgleda da mi stoji dobro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:44.66,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Horo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.64,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da. Dobro ime, ne misliš?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.00,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kakva slučajnost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:51.11,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poznat mi je neko ko nosi to ime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:56.11,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah? Ja ne znam nikog drugog sa tim imenom osim mene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:58.44,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Odakle je ta osoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:01.68,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je ime božanstva koje je generacijama obožavano u susednim selima.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:05.20,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li ti pokušavaš da kažeš da si bog?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:11.80,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mene smatraju bogom, i bila sam vezana za ovu zemlju dugo vremena,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.44,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ali nisam svemogući Bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.94,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja sam jednostavno Horo. Ništa više, ništa manje.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:21.60,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li si pomislio da sam sirota poremećena devojka
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:24.87,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}koja je celog života bila zatvorena u svojoj kući?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.48,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pomislio si, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.54,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja sam rođena na ravnicama severa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.42,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na severu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:34.48,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, na mestu gde su leta kratka a zime duge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:38.36,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moja domovina su šume Yoitsua,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:44.06,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}gde se sve blista, kao da je ceo svet od srebra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:54.03,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ti si putujući trgovac, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:56.67,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hoćeš li me povesti sa sobom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:58.63,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zašto bih?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:01.45,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja imam talenat da procenim ljude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:06.33,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vidim da nisi čovek hladnog srca koji bi odbio nečiju molbu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.34,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne približavaj se!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:10.04,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja nisam tako dobar čovek!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.76,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nećeš da budeš dobar prema meni?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.97,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tako si naivan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:21.43,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne mrzim ovo obličje, ali je previše hladno za mene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.75,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:36.84,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako si stvarno mudri vuk, Horo, dokaži mi to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:41.56,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Želiš da ti pokažem moje istinsko obličje?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:42.50,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.81,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne želim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:46.63,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Z-Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:48.27,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To mogu i ja tebe da pitam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:53.83,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, ako si ljudsko biće, predaću te crkvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.03,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Biti u društvu nekoga ko je posednut je loše.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.96,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali, ako si stvarno Horo, boginja žetve,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:04.80,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}razmislio bih o tvojoj molbi pošto bi mi mogla doneti sreću i bogatstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:11.23,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sigurno želiš da vidiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.54,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, želim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.97,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pitaću te još jednom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.98,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sigurno želiš da vidiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.36,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sigurno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:26.68,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Svaka promena obličja zahteva nekakvu nadoknadu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:30.52,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U mom slučaju to je ili krv života
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.96,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ili malo pšenice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:35.22,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možeš da koristiš pšenicu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.02,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.37,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta se dešava?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:17.15,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izvinite što sam se vratio tako iznenada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:21.78,Dialogue,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nije problem. Ja idem na festival a ti se možeš opustiti ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:29.87,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ko je?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:30.79,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:31.49,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Horo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.81,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pošto nisi došao po mene, ja sam došla po tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:41.38,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zar ne bi trebala da ostaneš u ambaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:44.62,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, ionako stvarna Horo ne postoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:46.08,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hajde, idemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:47.83,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gde idemo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:50.10,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zar nisi obećao da ćeš da me častiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:52.24,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mirišeš drugačije nego ranije.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.38,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da nisi trgovao u Sausbašeu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:56.15,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kao i uvek, imaš dobar nos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:15:00.51,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Miris svakog grada je lako razaznati, jednom kada ga upiješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.45,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I ti si se promenila.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:04.30,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgledaš samouvereno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:07.92,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zar ne? Prilično mi dobro ide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:10.97,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možda te i nadmašim uskoro, Lorens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:11.95,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.60,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Molim te da me unajmiš tada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.61,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kako si bezobrazan! Uopšte ne misliš tako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:19.71,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naravno da mislim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:21.60,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo piće je dobro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:26.30,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, hej. Lakše malo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:29.54,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako mi stvarno veruješ, imam interesantanu pogodbu za tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:34.85,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako stvari budu išle dobro, mogao bi imati svoju radnju i postati gazda jednog domaćinstva.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:38.12,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To zvuči neverovatno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.93,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne šalim se!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:44.46,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo je ogromna prilika, i postaćemo bogati ako sve bude išlo po planu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.01,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lorens?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:53.25,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sve više ličiš na svog oca.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:57.05,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}On je uvek preterivao kada se pričalo o poslu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.15,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali ovaj put nije tako.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.62,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zato govorim samo tebi, Lorens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:05.80,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Svaka dobra prilika nosi i dobru količinu problema sa sobom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:09.25,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zato hoćeš mene da unajmiš, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:14.79,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Želim da radim sa tobom zato što te poštujem, Lorens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:19.42,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lorens, stvari koje si me naučio sam urezala u srce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:22.61,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stigla sam do ovde zahvaljujući tebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.19,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sve je zahvaljujući tebi, Lorens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:31.70,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je opasno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.23,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Opasno, opasno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.70,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Još si mlada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:42.65,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Trebala bi da skupiš još iskustva pre nego što se oprobaš u sve-ili-ništa situacijama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.70,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dosadan si.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.53,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovakve prilike su retke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:52.59,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naći ću ti ja neki posao bez rizika sledeći put.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.40,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Onda možemo i zajedno da radimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:17:00.43,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I ja sam odrasla više nego što misliš.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:08.11,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Još imaš da učiš kao trgovac.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:12.53,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako ćeš da me tretiraš tako, osvetiću ti se jednog dana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.58,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Radujem se tom danu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.37,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Žena?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:21.58,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgledao si kao da si se izgubio u mislima.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.43,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li si našao boljeg partnera?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:27.55,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Samo sam se pitao kako bi bilo da mi je Horo partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.33,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Horo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:30.21,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pričaš o meni?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:32.69,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne, mislio sam na pravu Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.97,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kako uvrnuto. Imaš tako divlju maštu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:37.31,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maštu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.84,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maštu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.48,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maštu, ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:41.84,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, maštu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:46.05,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali šta ako Horo postoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:47.49,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Opet maštaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:49.23,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pitam se da li bi mogla da oseća tugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:51.27,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemoguće.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.11,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ipak je Horo bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:55.93,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U pravu si.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.88,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nema šanse da postoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.72,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Koga to tražiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.17,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:17.94,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nema potrebe da budeš iznenađen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.27,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gde si se krila?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:26.77,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U ovo doba, ja postojim u požnjetoj pšenici.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:30.69,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Obično ne mogu da se krećem odatle jer se dosta ljudi stara o žitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:33.08,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali postoji izuzetak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.20,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izuzetak?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:38.99,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako pored poslednjeg pokošenog svežnja postoji veći svežanj u blizini,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.98,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}mogu da pređem u njega.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:44.37,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, drugim rečima,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:50.29,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kako bih rekla? Ti si me spasao, moglo bi se reći.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:52.46,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Onda,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:55.51,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kada sam video tvoje istinsko obličje,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.41,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}nisam mogao da poverujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.04,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zato sam mislio da si nestala.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:24.24,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Davno, jedan mladić iz ovog sela me je zamolio za dobar rod žita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:27.12,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Od tada sam čuvala ova polja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:31.08,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali bogate žetve za redom će osiromašiti zemlju.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:33.63,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zato je ponekad potrebna siromašna žetva.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:38.36,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seljaci su krivili moju nepouzdanu prirodu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.96,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ozlojeđenost je rasla svake godine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:44.27,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nikome više nisam bila potrebna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:48.87,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čak i kada sam bila potrebna, svi su se plašili mog izgleda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.98,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Niko se nije usuđivao da mi priđe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:55.51,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To nije bilo ono što sam želela.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:04.60,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako za sada pretpostavimo da verujem u tvoju priču,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.05,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Baš si sumnjičav čovek.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:10.69,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}imaš li gde da odeš kada napustiš selo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.24,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Želim da se vratim na sever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:33.86,Dialogue,Chloe,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lorens!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:44.74,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U redu je. Možeš da izađeš sada.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:52.17,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bilo je teško vezati pertle pod ovime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:55.88,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa to je za očekivati...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:56.84,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pertle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:04.58,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, to je moja...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:07.26,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aha. Da li mi dobro stoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:09.82,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je moja najbolja odeća. Deset godina sam skupljao delove.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:10.92,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tako izgleda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:13.08,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kroj je divan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.03,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prilično si talentovan trgovac.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:19.03,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ili ćeš da skineš tu odeću i skloniš se odavde ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:21.22,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ti nisi vrsta čoveka koji bi ispratio tu pretnju.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.78,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zažalićeš ako me budeš potcenjivala.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:26.59,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, drago mi je što smo se upoznali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:27.70,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:28.87,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lorens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:30.66,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Craft Lorens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.77,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lorens, znači.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:38.69,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Od ovog trenutka nadalje, tvoje ime će postati legenda koja će odzvanjati kroz večnost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:44.56,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Umesto što pričaš bajke, koncentriši se na to da zaradiš za svoj hleb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.71,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo nije lak posao.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:51.00,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nisam toliko blesava da mislim da mogu da živim od tvog rada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:53.84,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja sam Horo, mudri vuk,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.96,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}i to vuk sa velikim ponosom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:59.48,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U svakom slučaju,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.69,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}malo je tesna.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:03.02,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:05.82,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa pretpostavljam da će me grejati što je dovoljno.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:26.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sedam jabuka na veštičinom drvetu,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:32.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,sa sedam semenki da zasadiš u meni.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:37.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,U proleće mi je narasla magična pesma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:44.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I onda, skakućući okolo, pevala sam je svima.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:48.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gledala sam svet kroz oči jabuke
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:53.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,i isekla sebi deo sunčane pite.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.86,0:22:59.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plesala sam sa kikiriki leptirovima
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:02.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dok nije došlo vreme i reklo mi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:05.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,da kažem zdravo ali mašem zbogom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.71,0:23:10.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiljadu šećernih zvezda.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:15.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stavi ih u teglu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:18.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I onda zviždući po svetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:21.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O, zviždući po svetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:25.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja sam mali vuk u devojci,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:26.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ti kažeš
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:31.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pređoh iz juna u maj."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:35.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O, zviždući po svetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:40.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajde da zviždućemo po svetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:52.05,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sledeća Epizoda: Vuk i daleka prošlost.
